A few days later, I was back in the park. I was hoping to see him again, but I didn't think I would.

I couldn't believe it. He remembered me!

We started talking and got to know each other better. I was so happy.

I was so happy! I couldn't wait to see him again.

We met up a few weeks later, and it was like nothing had changed. We were still as in love as ever.

I'm so happy that we found each other again. I can't imagine my life without him.
